前言關於英語史的科普小視頻，本系列分三集製作，歡迎觀看．
Episode I – The Indo-European Languages in the Pre-English Era  .embed-container {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  .embed-container iframe, .embed-container object, .embed-container embed {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }





